-content/uploads/2025/02/wutang_clan_four-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wutang_clan_four-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wutang_clan_four-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wu-tang-clan">Wu-Tang氏族</a>宣布了一张新专辑“ Black Samson，The Bastard Swordsman”，将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/record-store-day">2025年</a>发行。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="891" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2025-full-list-releases-vinyl-3835631"><b>唱片存储日2025：这是发行版的完整列表</b></a></li></ul><p>自2017年的 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rza-announces-new-album-wu-tang-saga-continues-2128914"><i>《传奇》（The Saga）</i></a>以来，传奇的嘻哈工作人员尚未发行全长专辑，但这将在4月12日的限量版运行中进行5000份新唱片的新唱片，这将在参与纪录的唱片店零售商中提供。</p><p>它看到Wu-tang与生产者数学团聚，后者自早期就一直与该小组联系在一起，并包括所有幸存的Wu-Tang成员的贡献，以及Kool G Rap，Kuroupt和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/benny-the-butcher">Butcher的Benny</a> 。</p><p>这张专辑将正式归功于“ Wu-Tang and Mathematics”，制片人说：“ Wu-Tang一直在音乐，艺术和文化上推动界限。凭借“黑人参孙，混蛋剑客”，我不仅为粉丝们提供专辑，而且还给粉丝们提供了一种历史，这确实是一种。”</p><p> “这不仅仅是音乐；这是创新，讲故事和遗产。我很高兴每个人都能听到音乐并围绕这张专辑观看艺术品。” </p><figure id="attachment_3835777" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3835777" style="width: 800px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3835777" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wu-tang-clan-black-samson-the-bastard-swordsman-artwork.jpg" alt="" width="800" height="800" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wu-tang-clan-black-samson-the-bastard-swordsman-artwork.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wu-tang-clan-black-samson-the-bastard-swordsman-artwork-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wu-tang-clan-black-samson-the-bastard-swordsman-artwork-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/wu-tang-clan-black-samson-the-bastard-swordsman-artwork-696x696.jpg 696w" sizes="(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3835777" class="wp-caption-text"> Wu-Tang和数学 - “ Black Samson，The Bastard Swordsman”封面艺术</figcaption></figure><h2><b>“黑人参孙，混蛋剑客”的曲目列表：</b> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="890" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <b>“免费城市”（壮举。</b> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="890" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;%1)&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"> <b>&#39;Mandingo&#39;（壮举。Raekwon，Inspectah Deck，Method Man和Cappadonna）</b> </li><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid="890" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:1,&quot;335552541&quot;:0,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-1,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769242&quot;:[65533,0,46],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&q